      "id": "PopularPost301382",
      "post_content": "0.5/5 because of the lolz.   \n  \nhttp://www.starcitygames.com/magic/extended/8378\\_The\\_Black\\_Perspective\\_Pro\\_Tour\\_Columbus.html  \n  \nIf a hate card like this is cast two turns in a row against the very type of deck that it's supposed to be hating, and that deck still manages to win, disgustingly.....then you are not a good hate card. XD  \n  \nIn order to be actually as relevant against Affinity as it needed to be, it needs to cost AT LEAST 1 less, but probably? Giving this card \"Affinity for Artifacts\" is what R&D should have done. :P Vorthos would have cried 'FOUL!' but everyone else should be ''grimly nodding'' or \"giggling hysterically\" at that idea.",
      "posted_by": "DarthParallax",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost301382\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">0.5/5 because of the lolz. <br/><br/>http://www.starcitygames.com/magic/extended/8378_The_Black_Perspective_Pro_Tour_Columbus.html<br/><br/>If a hate card like this is cast two turns in a row against the very type of deck that it's supposed to be hating, and that deck still manages to win, disgustingly.....then you are not a good hate card. XD<br/><br/>In order to be actually as relevant against Affinity as it needed to be, it needs to cost AT LEAST 1 less, but probably? Giving this card \"Affinity for Artifacts\" is what R&amp;D should have done. :P Vorthos would have cried 'FOUL!' but everyone else should be ''grimly nodding'' or \"giggling hysterically\" at that idea.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '301382'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy46041\">DarthParallax</span>\r\n                                (2/23/2013 1:06:57 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_